comment: Special group for demographic (quota cell) filters, such as age ranges, regions, genders, and SEGs; no other metrics should be added to this group, but I've added it here in case we should ever want to configure its order relative to other filter groups.
Note that the general quota cell (demographic) filters will always appear above this group.
Metric filters for which no group is explicitly specified will be added to this group, since it is the default. Note that there can be only one default filter group.
